      "text": "サニピはいつも、ここ一番の場面でめざましい力を\n発揮しますが……それにしてもこの点差は……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Sunny Peace always shows remarkable power\nwhen it matters most… but even so‚ this score difference is…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 77.2,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mhk",
      "speakerName": "miho",
      "speakerNameEn": "miho",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-miho.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_04_02_05/sud_vo_adv_main_04_02_05-mhk003.m4a",
      "text": "BIG4に昇格してさらなる高みで戦い続けるサニピと\n負けないように強敵を避け続けてきたトリエル……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Sunny Peace‚ who was promoted to BIG4 and fought at a higher level‚\nand TRINITYAiLE‚ who continued to avoid strong opponents so as not to lose…",
        "id": ""
