      "text": "サニピも月ストもリズノワも……BIG4になる者は\nみんなアイドルとしての核になるものを持っています",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Sunny Peace‚ Moon Tempest‚ and LizNoir… all of those who become the BIG4\nhave something that is the core of their idol life",
